.TH "nvme_init_get_log_boot_partition" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_boot_partition" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_boot_partition \- Initialize passthru command for Boot Partition
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_boot_partition
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u8 lsp "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_boot_partition *part "  ","
.BI "__u32 len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "lsp" 12
The log specified field of LID
.IP "part" 12
User address to store the log page
.IP "len" 12
The allocated size, minimum
struct nvme_boot_partition
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_BOOT_PARTITION
